And in Custom Bolt definition you will load the config:

```
class RabbitMQSpout(Bolt):
    def initialize(self, storm_conf, context):
        config_path = storm_conf.get('rabbitmq.configfile')
```

And you have "/etc/my_config.yml" string stored in config_path variable. From that, you can load the file or do whatever with this.

