  ]).then(([content]) => _mapContentSet(content), error => error);

  pagePrep.then(
    (recommendations, channels) => {
      if (!channels.length) {
        return;
      }
```

Possibly the intention was `pagePrep.then(([recommendations, channels]) => ...`, but the type of `pagePrep` looks like `Promise<Object>`, where `Object` is the return value of `_mapContentSet`. So maybe `pagePrep.then(({recommendations, channels}) => ...`?

